    {
      "id": "1968245864044843",
      "score": 1,
      "review_title": "Unplayable after update! 😠",
      "review_description": "This game seems to get worse after every update and now it's absolutely unplayable, at least on the Quest 3.\n\nAny movement causes a blurry double image.  I tried rebooting the headset to see if that would fix it.\n\nIt's infuriating when a developer either makes drastic changes to the gameplay or breaks their game with a bad update. They need to remember that people have paid for these games. It would be like if you bought a car and occasionally the manufacturer would sneak over to your driveway at night and repaint it color that you hate, swap out the dashboard for one that has the controls in all different places, or cut all your spark plug wires so the car won't start.",
      "date": 1772899052,
      "review_helpful_count": 19,
      "author_display_name": "Jioxx",
      "author_alias": "Jioxx",
      "developer_response": {
        "body": "Hey Jioxx, could you join the discord to share your experience? We're not seeing any other reports like this and haven't seen anything similar in testing. We're keen to support and improve the game.\n\nhttp://soulassembly.com/discord-dd",
        "date": 1773156987
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "1083630851498480",
      "score": 5,
      "review_title": "Ways to make your character stronger?",
      "review_description": "Are there any ways to get stronger after character level 21? I’ve upgraded a few weapon levels, but Hardcore mode is still too difficult for me to handle.\n\nWhere can I find new maps? What content is locked or unavailable to unlock?\n\nI’m really enjoying the game, but since I can’t get any stronger anymore, it’s starting to feel less fun over time.",
      "date": 1775919171,
      "review_helpful_count": 2,
      "author_display_name": "pennychoi",
      "author_alias": "pennychoi",
      "developer_response": {
        "body": "Hi, thanks for the review. Addressing your questions, direct from our wonderful QA folk:\n\n - Just upgrading weapon levels\n- Hardcore mode specifically disables all level perks and weapon level upgrades, so the only way to get better is to improve tactics/player skill\n(new maps?) - We have 3 focal points for the Cabin, one environment for Home Invasion, and 3 different environments for Last Stand.",
        "date": 1776845973
      }
    },
